These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving
There are 2 different nationalities: british, pakistani
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the british is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | gardening |
| Nationality   | british | pakistani    |
| Transport     | helicopter  | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, doctor
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the videographer##8
3. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | water    | mirinda    |
| Job   | videographer | doctor    |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, project-manager
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, french
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the french##8
2. the project-manager is not the french##6
3. the manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| Sport      | skateboarding   | climbing           |
| Job           | manager | project-manager |
| Nationality   | french  | australian      |

