1. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
2. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
3. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person traveling to prague##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Food          | zucchini  | grapes     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire    | scientific |
| City     | hamburg | prague      |

 